OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Ffine evening towards the east, but
OL,7,Fremaining rather cloudy near western
OL,8,Fcoasts, which will spread eastwards
OL,9,Fovernight. Some light rain and drizzle
OL,10,Fpossible over the hills, but most
OL,11,Fplaces staying dry.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAfter a cloudy start, cloud
OL,14,Fwill start to lift and break through
OL,15,Fthe morning. Prolonged sunny spells
OL,16,Fwill develop with some warm sunshine
OL,17,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
