OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure will bring a settled and
OL,7,Fincreasingly sunny and very warm spell
OL,8,Fof weather. Some cloud may affect
OL,9,Fcoastal areas at times, with sea
OL,10,Fbreezes also developing.
